==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Labadist
<hw>Lab"a*dist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Eccl. Hist.)</fld> <def>A
follower of <person>Jean de <etsep>Labadie</etsep></person>, a religious
teacher of the 17th century, who left the Roman Catholic Church and
taught a kind of mysticism, and the obligation of community of property
among Christians.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

